+From 95091b90c49a3e3dec9a5fe021e819a63f3dd743 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
+From: Codex <codex@openai.com>
+Date: Tue, 12 May 2026 15:04:33 +0000
+Subject: [PATCH] Signal-event funnel, anti-chase gates, wakeup detector, and
+ trading logic refinements
+
+### Motivation
+- Reduce false-positive and chase trades by adding an anti-chase timing gate and richer live tape quality checks.
+- Record full signal-event funnel to analyze where alerts/trades originate and measure conversion rates.
+- Improve position sizing, entry/exit behaviour and follow-through handling for both burst and scored trades.
+- Provide safer live execution by requiring an explicit live opt-in and validating wallet balance before auto-execution.
+
+### Description
+- Database: add `signal_events` table and indexes, plus `saveSignalEvent()` and `getSignalEVByType()` methods to record and summarize signal funnel metrics.
+- Core signal gating: add `evaluateAntiChaseGate()` and `saveSignalEvent()` helpers in `index.ts` and plug anti-chase checks into burst, stream, scored and live flows; record rejections/decisions to DB.
+- Burst detection: extend `BurstDetector` to compute `BurstMetrics` (15s/30s/60s volumes and acceleration) and apply liquidity-aware thresholds before confirming bursts.
+- Buy pressure: enrich `BuyPressureTracker` snapshots with acceleration, short-window volumes, top-buyer %, buyer concentration, repeat-buyer counts and wallet first-seen tracking.
+- Wakeup path: add `WakeupDetector` and wire a lightweight wakeup flow to detect dormant tokens that regain organic buying and route through the `TradeDecisionEngine`.
+- Paper/live execution: propagate `rawCurrency` through `TradeExecutor` and `PaperTrader`, add `getWalletXrpBalance()` to `TradeExecutor` and require wallet balance when making live auto-trades; improve AMM `OfferCreate` construction and parse flows.
+- PaperTrader enhancements: support approved/override sizes, add `followThroughScore` and adaptive take-profit/trailing logic, improve partial/close accounting and ghost-close handling, and register open positions for live price bypass.
+- Market/AMM: fix price parsing edge-cases in `MarketDataCollector`, add robust spread parsing helpers, and update `AMMPriceFetcher` cache bypass semantics for open positions.
+- Profiles & config: tune trade profiles in `execution/tradeProfiles.ts` and require an explicit `LIVE_EXECUTION_ACK` env value in `config.ts` to opt into real execution.
+- Analysis/logging: include profile-level stats in `TradeAnalyzer` summaries and append signal funnel stats to the periodic bot log.
+
+### Testing
+- Performed a TypeScript build (`npm run build`) to validate compilation and type changes, which completed without errors.
+- Ran linting (`npm run lint`) to verify formatting/static checks and fixed reported issues.
+- Exercised main runtime flows locally in `WATCH`/`PAPER` mode against a dev XRPL node to sanity-check burst/stream/wakeup gating and DB recording; signal event inserts and summary reads behaved as expected.
